Q2743\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Mis\\u00e9rables_(musical)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Mis\\u00e9rables_(musical)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following a sequence paying homage to the historical epic, French heavy metal band Gojira performed at the Conciergerie, a former courthouse and prison in the city.\", \"from\": 5116, \"to\": 5280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5175, \"end\": 5181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5569382399667312, \"rank\": 0.7946907777541343, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5199, \"end\": 5205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3786450041702553e-37, \"text\": \"Gojira\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\"}, {\"begin\": 5223, \"end\": 5235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.638051829388872e-44, \"text\": \"Conciergerie\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a nod to Louis Vuitton, a riverside Moulin Rouge can-can, a fashion runway, rap, ballet, a jet flyover and a beheaded Marie Antionette.\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5301, \"end\": 5314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.353790802886129e-38, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}, {\"begin\": 5328, \"end\": 5340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.881325333497653e-47, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}, {\"begin\": 5410, \"end\": 5426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marie Antionette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the other performers were pianist Alexandre Kantorow and French-Malian singer Aya Nakamura, who sang in a golden dress paired with gladiator boots and gold jewellery.\", \"from\": 5429, \"to\": 5601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5469, \"end\": 5487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Kantorow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alexandre Kantorow\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Kantorow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Kantorow\"}, {\"begin\": 5513, \"end\": 5525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aya_Nakamura\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aya Nakamura\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aya_Nakamura\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aya_Nakamura\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But perhaps the biggest cheer came for the French metal band Gojira who appeared on platforms high on the Conciergerie, an iconic building in the French Revolution, the first time a metal band had appeared at an Olympic opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5646, \"end\": 5652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5569382399667312, \"rank\": 0.7946907777541343, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5664, \"end\": 5670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3786450041702553e-37, \"text\": \"Gojira\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\"}, {\"begin\": 5709, \"end\": 5721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.638051829388872e-44, \"text\": \"Conciergerie\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conciergerie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The unprecedented ceremony sparked a colossal security operation in a city where memories of the November 2015 Islamist attacks are still raw.\", \"from\": 5842, \"to\": 5984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5953, \"end\": 5961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamism\", \"score\": 0.99905757973546, \"rank\": 0.0009428033714874949, \"text\": \"Islamist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 45,000 police and paramilitary officers were on duty to protect the ceremony, along with 10,000 soldiers and 22,000 private security guards.\", \"from\": 5986, \"to\": 6133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snipers, specialist frogmen, and AI-augmented cameras were deployed, with airspace closed and the area around the Seine virtually locked down.\", \"from\": 6135, \"to\": 6277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6249, \"end\": 6254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7095878462794958e-30, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"6min read  Published27 July 20249:22am  Updated27 July 20246:44pm  Source:Reuters